column5: Hey 4x4 I know no other way to get a hold of you.  you and Sally are more than welcome again this year to watch me almost burn the house down with the fondue.  He (4x4bassin) was a surprise guest last year and made me proud to be an OFNER.  KYLE, DANO you guys are probably not around...if you are I am at the corner of Crozier and Gier.  All the lights will be on!!!
They're all here Steve..send them a PM and it will pop up on their email to check in. Proper name spacing/spelling  4x4bassin kylem Dano
Also Steve, If your not shure you can click on the members tab top right corner and see who's here or not.....  Cheers !!
